title: P90X Complete [ISO,Ripped/tagged,Docs]
description:
This is the complete P90X system including all documentation, disc cover art, and screenshots that I use as digital cover art.

This torrent includes:
     Complete documentation
     Unofficial cover art
     Official disc cover art
     DVD ISO&#039;s (if you want to burn the DVD&#039;s)
     Ripped version (that will work on ipods, iPhones, computer, or apple TV - all completely tagged with cover art and ready to go)

I would like to give credit to all of those who have contributed to this package, but there were so many pieces that went into this that I no longer know who they are. Thanks to those contributors none the less.

If you want to save some time, you can grab the ripped versions rather than ISO&#039;s, They include the whole program and are high quality. The ripped version contains the music and training track. The ISO&#039;s allow you to turn off the music, but the music is not that bad. The choice is yours.

This is an excellent program and Tony Horton does a great job of being motivating without being annoying - (more so on P90X than P90X + - which I will be serving as well)
